Headstrong rises to his feet, as the gun blasts riddle his body, sending
him sidestepping backwards. He raised his gun to fire on his attackers,
but Firedrill grabs his legs, and trips him up. "*SNORT* You Autobots
never faught fair" Headstrong complained as he took to the air, and
headed away from the battl.
